item.title: About Me
item.description: I am a Jr. Software Developer who is aspiring to become a full-stack developer. I’m an optimistic, responsible, and hard-working person. I’m willing to dive into good projects no matter how pressure it is. I am able to enjoy working if there are only three C things: coffee, chocolate, and a computer. ☕ 🍫 💻 📗 Education Diploma in Computer Programmer, Seneca College CA, Sep 2017 - Dec 2018 Bachelor in Biomedical Science, Inje Univ KOR, Mar 2008 - Feb 2012 🏢 Work Jr.
